    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prevent schools from cancelling summer holidays due to coronavirus",
        "additional_details": "Many children have been provided work while off school or college while the corona virus has closed all teaching facilities, therefore I don't feel children are behind on learning as teachers are providing work/help online via their schools website.",
        "background": "Recently in the news it has been suggested that the summer holidays be cancelled to allow children to go back to school. However, people still working in schools through the outbreak need a break also. The summer holidays is also for children to have time off of school or college.",
